00:16:02,755 --> 00:16:04,576
<i>Namaku Kang Tae Wook.</i>

94
00:16:04,576 --> 00:16:05,786
<i>Apa pekerjaanmu?</i>

95
00:16:07,671 --> 00:16:09,476
<i>Aku seorang pengacara.</i>

96
00:16:09,476 --> 00:16:13,026
<i>Aku seorang pembela umum.</i>

97
00:16:14,966 --> 00:16:17,946
<i>Sudah berapa lama Kau
menikah dengan Nyonya Go Hye Ran?</i>

98
00:16:20,005 --> 00:16:21,776
Sudah 7 tahun.

99
00:16:21,776 --> 00:16:25,686
Bagaimana rumah tanggamu?

100
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:38,466
Kudengar Kau pergi menemui istrimu
di stasiun tv di hari kecelakaan itu.

101
00:16:38,466 --> 00:16:40,936
Apa benar?

102
00:16:40,936 --> 00:16:42,115
Ya, benar.

103
00:16:42,115 --> 00:16:44,166
Sekitar jam berapa?

104
00:16:44,166 --> 00:16:46,364
Aku bertemu dengannya setelah dia selesai siaran.

105
00:16:47,673 --> 00:16:49,412
