106
00:17:02,002 --> 00:17:04,368
<i>Apa Kau bersamanya
sepanjang waktu setelah itu?</i>

107
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:06,746
Maaf.

108
00:17:08,137 --> 00:17:09,586
Aku masih ada rapat.

109
00:17:10,738 --> 00:17:11,920
Aku harus pergi.

110
00:17:19,590 --> 00:17:20,630
Tidak.

111
00:17:22,456 --> 00:17:25,847
Sekitar jam berapa Go Hye Ran tiba di rumah?

112
00:17:26,857 --> 00:17:28,016
Aku tidak tahu.

113
00:17:29,607 --> 00:17:33,079
Aku masih ada pekerjaan malam itu,
jadi Aku di kantorku.

114
00:17:35,033 --> 00:17:36,476
Aku menginap di sana sepanjang malam.

115
00:17:38,455 --> 00:17:40,546
Kau berada di kantormu sepanjang malam?

116
00:17:40,546 --> 00:17:43,657
Ya, dia ada di kantor
ketika Aku tiba di sana.

117
00:17:43,657 --> 00:17:47,796
Saat dia banyak kerjaan,
dia sering bermalam di sana.

118
00:17:47,796 --> 00:17:51,321
Tepatnya jam berapa Kau
datang ke kantor?

119
00:17:51,321 --> 00:17:52,456
Aku tidak yakin, sih.

120
00:17:52,456 --> 00:17:57,197
Berita pagi yang memberitakan kasus
Kevin Lee, jadi...

121
00:17:57,197 --> 00:17:59,326
