217
00:25:57,472 --> 00:26:00,525
Pengacara Kang benar-benar tampan.

218
00:26:00,525 --> 00:26:04,634
Mengapa kita tidak melakukan
pemeriksaan fakta sekarang?

219
00:26:04,634 --> 00:26:09,664
